data.description: Picture yourself living on a private cul de sac with a lovely preserve view, your feet up on a lounge chair, basking besides your very own swimming pool.  Opportunity knocks for you to own this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home with vaulted ceilings and easy living.  The floor plan flows with split bedrooms and a galley kitchen with plenty of cabinets and pantry. Perfect for stirring up delicious meals.  Situated between the 2-car garage and kitchen, the inside laundry with utility sink adds practical convenience for busy families.  The living dining room combination is enhanced by sliding doors that pocket back seamlessly merging the indoor and outdoor screened space into one flowing living area. The front door is screened so you can open it allowing tropical breezes to flow through in winter months. Guess what? This neighborhood has sidewalks! You’ll love walking Fido and saying Hi to your neighbors. There are 2 associations, a Master and Neighborhood, but still the combined HOA fees are less than $73./mo. No CDD fees.  Best location in Sarasota county off University Parkway corridor.  Just a quick drive to reach Home Depot 1.4 mi,  Whole Foods 1.5mi, UTC Mall 2.5 mi the mecca for Shopaholics, SRQ Airport 5.5mi, to local beaches; Lido 11 mi and Siesta Key 18 mi. Make your dream a reality and schedule a tour today!
